    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&quot;Detective Support - Grow a Carrot&quot;</strong> is a <strong>DLC</strong> for <strong>&quot;Grow a Carrot&quot;</strong> in style of a visual novel with minigames! Explore bizzare lore of bunny island! Meet your favourite bunnies! Get to know who <strong>you</strong> are...</p><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238280/extras/bee3d17127cd059408f17c2126e08903.poster.avif?t=1733337816\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238280/extras/bee3d17127cd059408f17c2126e08903.webm?t=1733337816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>The DLC is divided into 9 short chapters with dialogues, each ending with a minigame. The entire DLC is in a point-and-click style, and offers  approximately 30 minutes of gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238280/extras/156a71d8428f09543bf6d3686e4a97ab.poster.avif?t=1733337816\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238280/extras/156a71d8428f09543bf6d3686e4a97ab.webm?t=1733337816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238280/extras/156a71d8428f09543bf6d3686e4a97ab.mp4?t=1733337816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Created in a pixel-art style with jazz playing in the background, it is designed to help you relax. <strong>&quot;Detective Support - Grow a Carrot&quot; DLC</strong> focuses mainly on the lore of Bunny Island and the player's backstory.<br><br>You wake up on Bunny Island, where <strong>Detective Support</strong> finds you. You go on an adventure across the island, uncovering the truth behind this mysterious place.<br><br>After finishing the <strong>DLC</strong>, you'll unlock chapter select, allowing you to replay your favorite chapter or re-read it if you missed something.",
